OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1774998182
OL,3,CDrug dealer in underpants who tried to
OL,4,Cescape police is jailed
OL,6,FPolice bodycam footage shows a
OL,7,FNottingham drug dealer, who ran an
OL,8,Fenterprise for six years, being
OL,9,Farrested in his underpants after
OL,10,Ftrying to run away from officers.
OL,12,FA drug dealer who was arrested in his
OL,13,Funderpants after trying to flee
OL,14,Fpolice, has been jailed for supplying
OL,15,Fheroin and cocaine while running a
OL,16,Fdrug enterprise for six years.
OL,18,FOfficers raided Andre McGowan's flat
OL,19,Fin Belconnen Road, Bestwood, when he
OL,20,Fjumped out of a first floor window in
OL,21,Fhis underwear.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
