CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1774998182
OL,3,CDrug dealer in underpants who tried to
OL,4,Cescape police is jailed
OL,6,FThe 36-year-old was detained moments
OL,7,Flater along a footpath outside the
OL,8,Fproperty and was arrested.
OL,10,FOfficers found an Aldi carrier bag
OL,11,Fcontaining heroin and crack cocaine
OL,12,Fwith a street value of up to #35,000.
OL,13,FIt was thrown into a garden by McGowan
OL,14,Fas he ran from police.
OL,16,FHis associate, Shabezz Wheeler-Spink,
OL,17,Fwas arrested at the same time in a
OL,18,Fsimultaneous warrant at a house in
OL,19,FNorton Street, Radford, where he was
OL,20,Fstaying.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1774998182
OL,3,CDrug dealer in underpants who tried to
OL,4,Cescape police is jailed
OL,6,FWheeler-Spink, 30, tried to destroy
OL,7,Fevidence as officers forced entry into
OL,8,Fhis partner's home.
OL,10,FHe was found flushing two plastic bags
OL,11,Fof heroin - worth #10,000 - down the
OL,12,Ftoilet, which then flooded the
OL,13,Fbathroom.
OL,15,FThe court heard Wheeler-Spink's
OL,16,Finvolvement in the drug enterprise
OL,17,Fspanned six months, mainly delivering
OL,18,Fdrugs to customers as instructed by
OL,19,FMcGowan.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
