FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1774998182
OL,3,CDrug dealer in underpants who tried to
OL,4,Cescape police is jailed
OL,6,FA police investigation was launched
OL,7,Fwhen information was received that an
OL,8,Festablished drugs line, known as the
OL,9,F"Vic Line", was operating in the
OL,10,FNottingham area.
OL,12,FDetectives found the line was owned
OL,13,Fand serviced predominantly by McGowan,
OL,14,Fwith Wheeler-Spink delivering drugs to
OL,15,Fcustomers at McGowan's instruction.
OL,17,FPolice say that McGowan was spending
OL,18,Fhis drug money on holidays
OL,19,Fdestinations such as Dubai and Turkey,
OL,20,Fwhile Wheeler-Spink took control of
OL,21,Fthe enterprise.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@JO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1774998182
OL,3,CDrug dealer in underpants who tried to
OL,4,Cescape police is jailed
OL,6,FFollowing today's sentencing,
OL,7,Finvestigating officer Liz Scott said:
OL,9,F"Illegal drugs bring real harm to our
OL,10,Fcommunities and anyone who thinks they
OL,11,Fcan profit from dealing controlled
OL,12,Fsubstances will be caught, arrested
OL,13,Fand put before the courts.
OL,15,F"In this case, McGowan thought he
OL,16,Fcould run from the police but failed
OL,17,Fspectacularly. By climbing out a first-
OL,18,Ffloor window in only his boxer shorts,
OL,19,Fhe grazed his feet while attempting to
OL,20,Fflee and had to be treated in hospital
OL,21,Fas a result.
OL,26,@qD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1774998182
OL,3,CDrug dealer in underpants who tried to
OL,4,Cescape police is jailed
OL,6,F"Wheeler-Spink's efforts to evade
OL,7,Fjustice were equally futile. It's
OL,8,Ffairly common for criminals to attempt
OL,9,Fto dispose of incriminating evidence
OL,10,Fwhen we arrive at their door ` and
OL,11,FWheeler-Spink certainly isn't the
OL,12,Ffirst drug dealer who has failed to
OL,13,Fflush drugs down a toilet.
OL,15,F"By contrast, our endeavours to flush
OL,16,Fout drugs operations like this one
OL,17,Fhave led to more prison sentences and
OL,18,Fwe are pleased to have added McGowan
OL,19,Fand Wheeler-Spink to a long list of
OL,20,Fdealers who have been brought to
OL,21,Fjustice in recent months."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU}D@ZO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/9
