PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1774998182
OL,3,CDrug dealer in underpants who tried to
OL,4,Cescape police is jailed
OL,6,FOther evidence seized during the
OL,7,Fwarrant at McGowan's flat included
OL,8,Fsignificant quantities of controlled
OL,9,Fdrugs and cash, along with a metal
OL,10,Fpress used to prepare and compress the
OL,11,Fdrugs.
OL,13,FOfficers were also able to seize
OL,14,Fassets belonging to McGowan including
OL,15,F#28,186 in crypto currency and bank
OL,16,Fassets.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1774998182
OL,3,CDrug dealer in underpants who tried to
OL,4,Cescape police is jailed
OL,6,FItems seized from the Radford address
OL,7,Fincluded the large amount of heroin
OL,8,FWheeler-Spink tried to flush down a
OL,9,Ftoilet, along with two lock knives, a
OL,10,Fdagger and a knife kept in a sheathe.
OL,11,FQuantities of cocaine and cannabis
OL,12,Fworth almost #12,000 were also seized.
OL,14,FMcGowan was jailed for 12 years.
OL,15,FWheeler-Spink, of Fenton Road,
OL,16,FBasford, Nottingham, was jailed for
OL,17,Fthree years.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/9
